	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Formam pacis ultimo submissam accepimus, ut ante monui, <placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Berna</placeName>; sed dubiam et supposititiam omnino esse arbitror; nam praeteritis diebus singularis meus amicus rediit in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2498" cert="high">Germaniam</placeName>, qui toto belli tempore cum principe fuit et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l367" cert="high">Aurelia</placeName> digressus est mense aprilis.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Is ad me literas dedit, cuius exemplum hic ad te mitto Germanicum; plus huic tribuo fidei quam ullis aliis.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Est praeterea satelles quidam regis, qui consuli nostro amplissimo d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p3493">a Chaam</persName> ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l378" cert="high">Lutetia</placeName> mense aprilis paria prope scripsit, nisi quod in suis addit <persName type="citizen_name">regem Germano</persName> equitatui persoluturum stipendia et pacem coiisse bonam, solos Guisianos subinde moliri nova.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus coherceat eos!</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Festinanter haec scripsi; tu haec boni consulas, oro.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuas literas accepi per amplissimum hunc doctorem, virum optimum.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Utinam ignis verbi dei in regno papae ardeat et antichristum consumat!</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si quid aliud et amplius accepero, mature significabo.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid, oro, fit cum <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8441">Schvenckfeldianis</persName> etc.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Optime vale cum uxore et liberis et amicis omnibus, d. d.d consulibus, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p20473" cert="high">Ganthnero</persName>, <persName ref="p6130" cert="high">Pontisella</persName> et reliquis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tiguri</placeName>, 10. maii 1568.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Bullingerus</persName> tuissimus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Der gwardiknächt schript ouch minem herren <persName type="citizen_name">von Chaam</persName>, daß der könig yngesetz habe <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l322" cert="high">Metz</placeName>, <placeName ref="l503" cert="high">Thun</placeName>, <placeName ref="l1920" cert="high">Verdun</placeName> etc. und das ein sorg syge, groß krieg werde sich erheben imm <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l20">Niderland</placeName> wider duca <persName type="citizen_name">de Alba</persName>, den die <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l20">Niderländer</placeName> nemmend duck dich an galgen.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hoc non satelles addit, sed ego ex literis ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l808">Belgio</placeName> allati<note type="margin">dazu a.R.: Hoc - allatis Zus. a.R. auf d. Zus v. "wider" an bezügl., urspr. hinter "Niderland" ein Punkt.</note>.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ornatissimo viro d. <persName ref="p8016" cert="high">Thobiae Eglio</persName>, <placeName ref="l98" cert="high">Curiensis</placeName> ecclesiae fideli ministro, domino colendo et fratri charissimo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Chur.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
